A JSON/REST search server.

 * Source: http://github.com/rboulton/restpose
 * Documentation: http://restpose.readthedocs.org/

There is a python client for RestPose:

 * Source: http://github.com/rboulton/restpose-py
 * Documentation: http://restpose-py.readthedocs.org

This project is still at an early stage of development.  No releases have
been made yet, though the first public release is imminent.  Chat to
rboulton on irc://irc.freenode.net/#restpose (in a browser:
http://webchat.freenode.net/?channels=#restpose) or @rboulton on
identica/twitter for further information.
